posting_body: ['Large corner South West facing one bedroom in The West Village on Jane st.', 'Listing ID #: 137990', 'Price: $6,226', 'Broker Fee apartment', 'Property Type: Apartment', 'Bedrooms: 1.0', 'Bathrooms: 1.0', 'Virtual Tour: Click to view', 'Building Amenities', 'Doorman', 'Elevator', 'Laundry', 'Apartment Amenities', 'Dishwasher', 'Renovated', 'Light', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Gorgeous, Large corner South West facing one bedroom with tons of windows and Sunny City Views on a quiet West Village street in a luxury building!', 'Kitchen renovations include quartz counter tops and stainless steel appliances.', 'Steps from Meatpacking and West village restaurants and nightlife but far enough from the crowds and noise.', 'Please note this is a lease assignment from August 1 to February 28, 2023 with option to renew after for a new 12 month lease or do a 12 month lease since the beginning.', 'Current tenant is open to selling most of his furniture for a good price if anyone is interested.', 'Contact me for more information.', 'Alex Caballero', 'Phone: 210-885-1767', 'Mobile: 210-885-1767', 'Fax: 212-962-3970', 'Email: <URL>', 'New York Living Solutions - Keller Williams New York City \xa0 210-885-1767 \xa0 210-885-1767 \xa0 FAX 212-962-3970 \xa0 <URL>', 'POSTED BY REALTYMX™', 'To view, call or text Alex Caballero at 210-885-1767']
